messages.content: It’s not so much a house as it is a *tree*house, but Wanderer excitedly carries the notebook inside. “OK! W-Were here!”
@Caeli @Heliotrope
Woah, it looks great!
“Th-Thanks! I think it took two millennia to build, and it’s built f-from all different kinds of wood from different universes!”
Huh ne- wait, millenia! It took 2000 years?!
“Oh, did I say millennia? ...I meant two *hundred thousand* years.”
WHAT?! W-why?
~~even I don't procrastinate that much~~
“W-Well, every 100,000 human years is one mun year.”
She tilted her head. She has no concept of time
“Basically, Time moves *way* faster here than it does on earth.”
Oh, interesting!
“S-So Basically, in our time it only took two years to build.” She finished, placing the book on a table.
Among the things in the treehouse was a duffel bag, a set of notebooks and paint, a few gaming systems which seemed to come from different universes, and an acoustic guitar.
Wow, cool place!
“Th-Thanks!” She smiled.
Are you exicted Rassy? You're gonna get your own tesseract!
“R-Really? She is?”
She nodded excitedly
Yeah! Juri's gonna get her one!
We don't have to pay her back or anything!
“W-Wow, really?”
“That’s really nice of her!”
I know right!
“There’s a lot of stuff these things can do, Y’know.” She said, holding up her red tesseract cube.
Really? Like what? I thought you could just text and stuff.
“W-Well, you know what FaceTime is, right?”
Sort of. It's like a call, but you can see the other person, right?
“W-Well, you can do that, not just for other people...but for yourself.”
...So I can talk with myself?
“Yeah! L-Let me show you!” She pushes a few buttons and a human Joss appears!
Woah! Hi Joss! Wow, she looks small compared to you.
“I know, right?” Both of them said together.
*he giggles*
“I-I don’t look that different from what you’re used to...r-right?” The human asked.
Nope! Not at all!
She sighed in relief.
@Gekitoutsu Rispba //Raspberry needs a tesseract.
There’s a shake of the tree. “Special delivery.”
Juri! You're here!
“‘Sup!”
How are you doing? Hey Rassy, look, Juri has your tesseract!
She popped her head put of the book again "YAY!!!!!" She grabs it with her tail
Rodophis gasped when Raspberry grabs her  tesseract.
"Sorry!!!!! Im excited to talk to everyone!!!!"
“You’re cool, you’re cool.”
Wait. I got thought of something. Wanderer mentioned that we could bring out other versions of ourselves, right?
“Y-Yeah? What’s your point?” Joss asked.
Two Rassys is my point.
“...Oh...” she nodded.
Raspberry tilted her head.
“J-Just as an FYI, the copies are United.”
O-oh. H-has she been united yet?
“No, not like that. They’re copies, already United.” She whispered.
oh, got it.
Do we need to set it up or something?
“Yeah, but it’s not hard. Just a hand scan.”
Alright!
“Tell her to place her claw on top of the cube.”
@Pastel warrior of hope!!!
She does as she was told!
“There, that should do it.” Rodophis smiles.
thank you again!
“No problem!” She said, before leaving.
“O-Oh! There’s another cool thing these can do!”
Like what?
She tapped a button. “Make a stuffed Dalmatian!” She said clearly, and slowly it manifested through the side of the cube.
woah! It can make stuff!
“Yeah-isn’t it c-cool?”
Very! Hey Rassy, check it out!
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
She tilted her head with an OwO? look on her face
What button do you tap, Wanderer?
“This one, then say what you want in a strong voice.”
Ok! *he pushes the button* Make me a candy bar!
*a candy bar manifests, which he hands to Raspberry*
Here you go Rassy!
@Pastel warrior of hope!!!
Her tail wagged "Yummy!!!!!!"
*he smiles and giggles* Glad you like it!
“I-I’m glad you got someone you love, Time Warp...”
I am too! You seem to be good friends with Caeli!
Oooo, I thought of something!
“Wh-What’s that?”
*he presses the button* Make me a hoverpad. *a hoverpad is made that can fit the notebook*
“Ohh...w-wait, what’s your plan?”
we can use that to go places without needing help!
“Oh! Clever!”
Thank you! Can you put us on it please?
She nodded, setting the notebook on it.
thank you!
“Y-You’re welcome!”
“O-Oh! Want to join my family’s chat?”
Of course! Can Rassy join?
“Sure!”
Yay!
"Hey Rassy, I just thought of a fun idea!"
She tilted her head "Whats up???"
"So, you know how my notebook is on a hoverboard right?"
She nodded
"and how I can take things out of the notebook, right?"
She nodded
"Well, I was thinking, what if we dropped water balloons on people?"
"Ooooo!!! That sounds like fun!"
"I thought so too! Who should we get first?"
"Uhh....Juri!!!!" She giggled
"Alright! Let's see if we can find her!"
She nodded
*he starts hovering around and looks for  juri*
oh, what if we did wanderer first?
//they don't know the name change, probably
"Oooo! Yeah!"
"Hey, wanderer!" he giggles a little
“H-Hmm?”
he drops a water balloon on them.
“AAH!” She shuddered.
he giggles and high fives raspberry.
he floats down to aion "Surprise!
“T-Time Warp, you scared me...”
"oh, sorry! We just wanted to prank you!"
“I-It’s fine, it was harmless...
"Anyway, Rassy and I are gonna drop water balloons on muns!"
“W-Well, OK...”
he hands aion a water balloon
She took it. “I-I dunno...I’m not a very good aim...”
"I'm sure you can hit something!"
“I...guess I can try...”
Aion is back in her treehouse.
( @Radioactive Lain )
radium flew up to aion's treehouse and looked in "hello ?... is aion here ?"
She glanced up at her. “Wh-Who are you...?”
"call me radium, I'm here for the goop"
Her eyes widened. “N-No...” She trembled, wrapping her tail around her. “Momo said she wanted to stay with me.”
she sighed, rubbing her forehead "I made a deal with the goop, it get out of the hosts' bodies, and I make one for it. Once it will have a body, you'll be able to see eachother whenever !"
She still looked nervous.
(Is Momo still in clone Aion?
(Yeah I imagine)
Momo hid behind Aion "G-Go away!!!"
“Y-Yeah! You heard her!”
"Please, don't make my job *harder* here. I told you, I can make a body just for you, alright? A custom one"
"Aion made a clone for us! We dont want her to be alone....." shes still hiding
"Hey, it'll just be temporary! I can make as many bodies as need, and in every way you'd like, you two will be back together in no time !" she tried to give a smile, but she looked *tired*
“P-Promise...?”
she nodded "promise" while she wasn't lying, she knew that making a body would take a *lot* of time. *oh well*, she'll deal with that problem later
Momo was hugging Aion tightly "Why do we need to leave now? Why cant we stay here until the body is ready??"
“Y-Yeah!” Aion said, tail swishing back and forth.

"because you've caused *enough* trouble. You never were supposed to leave the lab, and I don't know how much you can do. It would be for the best to keep you in the lab until the body is ready, for security"
“She’s not causing trouble!”
"We aren't leaving!"

"**Listen**" she got closer to the two "I don't know how powerful you can be, or how you behave, for all I know, you could *attack* someone at any point. It's for everyone's security that you would go to the lab" She was getting fustrated
"Im not gonna attack anyone! Im just going to hang out with Aion!" Momo huffed

"Look, I *didn't* know you were sentient, meaning that you're full of surprises, and therefore you're unpredictable. If you want to keep *this* body so bad, I'll allow it, since it looks like it's a harmeless clone. However, you'll have to stay in the lab"
"Its not the body its the fact I wanna stay with Aion!!"

She rolled her eyes "Oh come *on* you could tolerate a little time spent away from her, no? at the very *worst* she can come for a visit, even if I'd prefer not seeing any muns near my lab, I'm *willing* to make an exception"
".....Fine...Thats acceptable...."
Aion just nodded, looking saddened.
She clapped her hands, giving a tired smile "Good, good ! now I guess you'll have to follow me, unless you're willing to give up that body and join the rest"
“I’ll... miss you, Momo.”
"Ill miss you too Aion...." She smiles sadly, starting to cry a bit
She hugged her, sniffling.
She sighed, touched by the mun and the goop. "Alright... let's get to the lab, come on " she tapped the rock she was on.
Momo sniffled and got on "Byebye friend...."
“B-Bye...” she waved back.
She gave the two a sadden and tired look before flying off to her lab
